{"data":[{"name":"79:1","price":"By those who pull out [evil souls][1] harshly,","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰزِعَٰتِ غَرۡقٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5713,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1] Of the disbelievers.","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:2","price":"and by those who draw out [good souls][2] gently,","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِطَٰتِ نَشۡطٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5714,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[2] Of the believers.","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:3","price":"and by those who glide swiftly[3],","arabic":"وَٱلسَّٰبِحَٰتِ سَبۡحٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5715,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[3] i.e., angels glide swiftly through the heavens and earth with Allah’s command.","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:4","price":"and those who overtake one another as in a race[4],","arabic":"فَٱلسَّٰبِقَٰتِ سَبۡقٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5716,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[4] To execute Allah's commands.","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:5","price":"and those who carry out the command [of Allah],","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُدَبِّرَٰتِ أَمۡرٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5717,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:6","price":"on the Day when the earth convulses [by the first Blast],","arabic":"يَوۡمَ تَرۡجُفُ ٱلرَّاجِفَةُ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5718,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:7","price":"followed by the second Blast,","arabic":"تَتۡبَعُهَا ٱلرَّادِفَةُ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5719,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:8","price":"hearts[5] will be pounding on that Day,","arabic":"قُلُوبٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ وَاجِفَةٌ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5720,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[5] Of those who denied the Resurrection.","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:9","price":"and their eyes[6] will be downcast.","arabic":"أَبۡصَٰرُهَا خَٰشِعَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5721,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[6] Of the disbelievers.","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:10","price":"They say, “Will we be brought back to life,","arabic":"يَقُولُونَ أَءِنَّا لَمَرۡدُودُونَ فِي ٱلۡحَافِرَةِ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5722,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:11","price":"after we have turned into decayed bones[7]?”","arabic":"أَءِذَا كُنَّا عِظَٰمٗا نَّخِرَةٗ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5723,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[7] They would say this in ridicule of the warning.","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:12","price":"They say, “Then that would surely be a losing return[8]!”","arabic":"قَالُواْ تِلۡكَ إِذٗا كَرَّةٌ خَاسِرَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5724,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[8] To one another.","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:13","price":"It will only be a single Blast,","arabic":"فَإِنَّمَا هِيَ زَجۡرَةٞ وَٰحِدَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5725,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:14","price":"then they will immediately be above the ground.","arabic":"فَإِذَا هُم بِٱلسَّاهِرَةِ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5726,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:15","price":"Has there come to you the story of Moses,","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ مُوسَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5727,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:16","price":"when his Lord called out to him at the sacred valley of Tuwa?","arabic":"إِذۡ نَادَىٰهُ رَبُّهُۥ بِٱلۡوَادِ ٱلۡمُقَدَّسِ طُوًى","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5728,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:17","price":"[Saying,] “Go to Pharaoh, for he has transgressed all bounds”.","arabic":"ٱذۡهَبۡ إِلَىٰ فِرۡعَوۡنَ إِنَّهُۥ طَغَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5729,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:18","price":"And say: ‘Are you willing to be purified,","arabic":"فَقُلۡ هَل لَّكَ إِلَىٰٓ أَن تَزَكَّىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5730,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:19","price":"and I will guide you to your Lord so that you may fear Him?’”","arabic":"وَأَهۡدِيَكَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَتَخۡشَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5731,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:20","price":"Then Moses showed him the greatest sign[9].","arabic":"فَأَرَىٰهُ ٱلۡأٓيَةَ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5732,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[9] i.e., the miracle of the staff turning into a snake. See 20:17-23.","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:21","price":"But Pharaoh denied it and disobeyed.","arabic":"فَكَذَّبَ وَعَصَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5733,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:22","price":"Then he turned back striving to plot.","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَدۡبَرَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5734,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:23","price":"He gathered [his people] and proclaimed,","arabic":"فَحَشَرَ فَنَادَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5735,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:24","price":"saying, “I am your lord, the most high.”","arabic":"فَقَالَ أَنَا۠ رَبُّكُمُ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5736,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:25","price":"So Allah seized him for an exemplary punishment in this life and in the Hereafter[10].","arabic":"فَأَخَذَهُ ٱللَّهُ نَكَالَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةِ وَٱلۡأُولَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5737,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[10] Or for his claim of being the greatest god and for his previous oppression of the Children of Israel.","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:26","price":"Indeed, there is a lesson in this for those who fear Allah.","arabic":"إِنَّ فِي ذَٰلِكَ لَعِبۡرَةٗ لِّمَن يَخۡشَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5738,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:27","price":"Are you more difficult to create or the heaven that He built?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ أَشَدُّ خَلۡقًا أَمِ ٱلسَّمَآءُۚ بَنَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5739,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:28","price":"He raised its vault high and proportioned it,","arabic":"رَفَعَ سَمۡكَهَا فَسَوَّىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5740,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:29","price":"and darkened its night and brought forth its daylight.","arabic":"وَأَغۡطَشَ لَيۡلَهَا وَأَخۡرَجَ ضُحَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5741,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:30","price":"And thereafter He spread out the earth,","arabic":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضَ بَعۡدَ ذَٰلِكَ دَحَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5742,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:31","price":"brought forth from it its water and its pasture,","arabic":"أَخۡرَجَ مِنۡهَا مَآءَهَا وَمَرۡعَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5743,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:32","price":"and set the mountains firmly,","arabic":"وَٱلۡجِبَالَ أَرۡسَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5744,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:33","price":"as a provision for you and your grazing livestock.","arabic":"مَتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5745,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:34","price":"But when the Supreme Calamity comes[11],","arabic":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلطَّآمَّةُ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5746,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[11] i.e., the second Blast which marks the Day of judgment.","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:35","price":"on that Day man will remember all what he did,","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَتَذَكَّرُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَا سَعَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5747,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:36","price":"and the Blazing Fire will be exposed for all to see.","arabic":"وَبُرِّزَتِ ٱلۡجَحِيمُ لِمَن يَرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5748,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:37","price":"As for those who transgressed,","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَن طَغَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5749,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:38","price":"and preferred the life of this world,","arabic":"وَءَاثَرَ ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5750,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:39","price":"the Blazing Fire will be their abode.","arabic":"فَإِنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ هِيَ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5751,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:40","price":"But those who feared standing before their Lord and restrained themselves from evil desires,","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَافَ مَقَامَ رَبِّهِۦ وَنَهَى ٱلنَّفۡسَ عَنِ ٱلۡهَوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5752,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:41","price":"Paradise will surely be their abode.","arabic":"فَإِنَّ ٱلۡجَنَّةَ هِيَ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5753,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:42","price":"They ask you concerning the Hour, “When will it be[12]?”","arabic":"يَسۡـَٔلُونَكَ عَنِ ٱلسَّاعَةِ أَيَّانَ مُرۡسَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5754,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[12] Lit., \"established.\"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:43","price":"How could you possibly mention that?","arabic":"فِيمَ أَنتَ مِن ذِكۡرَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5755,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:44","price":"Its knowledge rests only with your Lord[13].","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ مُنتَهَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5756,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[13] i.e., its end and termination. Its ultimate knowledge belongs to Allah alone.","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:45","price":"You are only a warner for those who fear it.","arabic":"إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُنذِرُ مَن يَخۡشَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5757,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"79:46","price":"On the Day when they see it[14], it will be as if they had remained [in this world] no more than an evening or a morning.","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُمۡ يَوۡمَ يَرَوۡنَهَا لَمۡ يَلۡبَثُوٓاْ إِلَّا عَشِيَّةً أَوۡ ضُحَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5758,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[14] i.e., the Hour.","lang":"en"}],"chapter":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at","Chapter An-Nazi'at","Nazi'at","Surah Nazi'at","Chapter Nazi'at","An Nazi'at","Surah An Nazi'at","Chapter An Nazi'at","Surah 79","Chapter 79","Those Who Pull Out","النازعات"]}